<subSubSection pageId="19" pageNumber="20" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="19.[151,1437,434,1220]" pageId="19" pageNumber="20">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,359,1154,1180]" pageId="19" pageNumber="20">Distribution.</emphasis>
A rarely collected species known only from 
<collectingCountry box="[893,1002,1154,1180]" name="Germany" pageId="19" pageNumber="20">Germany</collectingCountry>
(Berlin area), 
<collectingCountry box="[1176,1257,1154,1180]" name="Poland" pageId="19" pageNumber="20">Poland</collectingCountry>
(Warsaw area) and as new from 
<collectingCountry box="[353,431,1194,1220]" name="Russia" pageId="19" pageNumber="20">Russia</collectingCountry>
(East Karelia).
</paragraph>
